# E-Commerce DevOps Project

## Overview
End-to-end DevOps and GitOps implementation for a full-stack e-commerce application deployed on AWS.

## Tech Stack
- AWS EC2
- Docker
- Jenkins (CI)
- Kubernetes
- Argo CD (GitOps CD)
- NGINX Ingress

## What I Worked On
- Containerization of frontend, backend, and database
- CI pipelines using Jenkins
- GitOps-based deployments with Argo CD
- Kubernetes deployments and ingress configuration
- Production-style debugging and stability fixes

